article.description: — Ryan Hawkins had a season-high 30 points plus 12 rebounds as Creighton beat Georgetown 80-66 on Saturday.
article.headline: Hawkins scores 30 to carry Creighton over Georgetown 80-66
article.linkText: Hawkins scores 30 to carry Creighton over Georgetown 80-66
article.story: WASHINGTON -- — Ryan Hawkins had a season-high 30 points plus 12 rebounds as Creighton beat Georgetown 80-66 on Saturday. Ryan Kalkbrenner scored a career-high 22 points and had 15 rebounds for Creighton (15-8, 7-5 Big East Conference). Trey Alexander added six assists. Ryan Nembhard and Hawkins had seven assists. Creighton posted a season-high 26 assists. Kaiden Rice had 16 points for the Hoyas (6-17, 0-12), whose losing streak reached 13 games. Donald Carey added 16 points and seven rebounds. Aminu Mohammed had 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
